{
  "texts": [
    "We used a spike-in experiment of different concentrations ranging from 7% to 28% VAF of HG002 into high coverage of HG00733.",
    "Figure 4a,b shows the precision and recall of SVs across the different concentrations.",
    "Overall, Sniffles2 mosaic mode outperforms the other SV calling approaches.",
    "The recall is impacted by the fact that the subsampling occurs randomly and that heterozygous SVs are disproportionately sampled.",
    "Correcting for this fact and measuring recall on SVs occurring within 5-25% VAF improved the recall for Sniffles2 mosaic mode, as it averages 94.47% given an overall 84.12% precision."
  ]
}